title: Assassin's Creed- Prestige 99 Generator (Alpha 2.0.0)
description:
Assassin's Creed is a historical fiction action-adventure open world stealth video game series that consists of five main games and a number of supporting materials, as of 2013. The games have appeared on the PlayStation 3, Xbox 360, Microsoft Windows, Mac OS X, Nintendo DS, PlayStation Portable, PlayStation Vita, iOS, HP webOS,Android, Nokia Symbian Windows Phone platforms, and the Wii U.




Note- This works for the PC, PS3, Xbox360, as well as the Wii U. This is
compatible with Assassin's Creed Brotherhood,Assassin's Creed Revelation, Assassin's Creed 3, and Assassin's Creed Black flag, once it releases. Have fun! :D
